description:
We talk to Blake Shelton about if he’s doing a duets album with Gwen, his first no. 1 and he grills Bobby a bit about his girlfriend. Bobby asks if anyone would take this coin flip challenge. Heads you win $100, tails you shave an eyebrow. Why Lunchbox has to call the cops on someone...
